Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.43,0:01:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.70,0:01:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走进过这扇大门的有不少海底生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Through these doors
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pass all the many kinds of undersea life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走进大门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Through the double doors
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.22,0:01:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及这两位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Also these guys
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.15,0:01:18.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都跟你说了我不饿  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:18.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you I'm not hungry, Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.95,0:01:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense, Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.10,0:01:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要强身健体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to keep up our strength
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.12,0:01:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才有力气对抗邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the fight against evil
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.25,0:01:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太破烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a dive
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.84,0:01:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往收银台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the register
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.32,0:01:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.10,0:01:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.65,0:01:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来个双层蟹黄堡和珊瑚块
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A double Krabby Patty and coral bits for me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.30,0:01:39.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给小的来个笨笨套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:39.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a Silly Meal for the lad
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是想要玩具  只是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not for the toy, I just, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要保持身材穿紧身衣  懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta fit in the tights, you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.07,0:01:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请付五块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five dollars, please
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.67,0:01:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it, Bucky
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.87,0:01:52.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么多够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:52.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will this cover it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.97,0:01:55.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:55.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.38,0:01:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  大鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, Big Nose
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.27,0:02:00.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那人自从你出生之前就在救你命了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:58.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy's been saving your butt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,since before you were born
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,传奇人物就没个优惠什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you got a Living Legend discount or something?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是家饭店  不是图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a restaurant, not a lending library
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你管谁叫大鼻子  大鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And who're you calling Big Nose, Big Nose?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下次危机到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The next time danger threatens
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就别指望我们会救你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't expect any help from us
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怕死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm shaking
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.30,0:02:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还美人鱼战士企鹅男孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.03,0:02:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.82,0:02:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.70,0:02:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,签名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,autograph
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.81,0:02:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想长得跟我一样壮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want to grow up strong like me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得留个几秒腾出空间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you gotta make room for seconds
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.54,0:02:45.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,服务生来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:45.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes our waiter
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,签
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Auto
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,graph
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  是那个海绵小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy sea cow, it's that sponge kid
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick lad
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.79,0:02:55.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往无影船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:55.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the invisible boat mobile
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Away
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船停哪来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd we park?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能找你们签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have your autograph?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能找你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have your?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're gone
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士的腰带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman's belt
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用无影船钥匙警报就能找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll find it with the invisible boat alarm
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.05,0:03:16.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船在那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:16.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There she is
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早跟你说得开自动挡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you we should've got the automatic
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, wait up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.39,0:03:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有东西要给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got something for you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油门踩到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Floor it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.01,0:03:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们忘拿腰带了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot your belt
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们忘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士的秘密多用途腰带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman's secret utility belt
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底正义的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The emblem of submersible justice
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六十五年来  这个腰带协助防止了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For 65 years, this belt has helped prevent
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各国的覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the fall of nations
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有走光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And pants
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.54,0:03:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它居然到了我的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm actually holding it in my hands
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该得还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I should return it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or not
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.04,0:04:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班期间我可以好好保管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could just hold on to it until after work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.38,0:04:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟美人鱼战士的腰带独处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All alone with Mermaidman's belt
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道这按钮干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what this button does
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,缩小射线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The small ray
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的奶昔  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your shake, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎下次再来  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come again, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么东西全变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is everything all tiny?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.84,0:04:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你身上什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have you got?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.72,0:04:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, really
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.50,0:04:50.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:50.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.30,0:04:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定藏了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got something all right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.04,0:04:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是美人鱼战士的腰带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that Mermaidman's belt?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.25,0:04:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信他居然会借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he'd lend it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.65,0:05:03.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:03.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,either
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.81,0:05:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意应该不是他借你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He didn't lend it to you, did he?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托别告状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你偷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stole it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托别告状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要告状了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  让美人鱼战士发现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, If Mermaidman finds out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定会把我踢出粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he'll kick me out of his fan club for sure
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托别告状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在朝着电话走过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm walking towards the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.09,0:05:24.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:24.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我离电话越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting closer to the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.97,0:05:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是万众期待的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for the moment we've all been waiting for
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想找美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak to Mer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.07,0:05:43.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.41,0:05:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.97,0:05:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you do to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  都是你逼我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you made me do it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是不马上把我恢复成正常大小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you don't return me to normal size right now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就真的要惹上大麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you are going to be in really big trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说马上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见了没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鬼东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy fish paste
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it off me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it off me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不会用那东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you know how to work that thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.26,0:06:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打电话找美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's call Mermaidman and
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让你这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't let you do that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定有谁可以帮的上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But there must be someone else who can help
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,聪明有智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone smart and wise
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有多年的阅历
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with years of life experience
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.13,0:06:58.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:58.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我刚在上班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I was at work
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Mermaidman and Barnacleboy came
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就有了这腰带  然后你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I got this belt and look
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥手办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Squidward action figure
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我玩他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me play with him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,战斗机飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fighter pilot
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dive bomb
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.55,0:07:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.07,0:07:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后吃我一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then comes a giant fist
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是手办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not an action figure
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's the real Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不小心缩小他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shrunk him by accident
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也吃我一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then comes a giant
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, you don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is serious
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么办才能放大回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to un-shrink him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能他后半辈子都只能这么小了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He could be stuck like this for the rest of his life
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他总有一天会找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll find love one day
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.12,0:07:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  不过对象得跟他差不多大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, but it'll be with someone his own size
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如这个腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this pickle
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们相亲相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They like each other
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.72,0:07:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我会用这东西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only I knew how to work this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道问题出在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what the problem is?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把它设置成了M  表示小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it set to "M", for mini
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该得设置成W  表示巨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When it should be set to "W", for "wumbo"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  巨好像有些意义不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I don't think "wumbo" is a real word
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我巨  你巨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wumbo, you wumbo
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他她我巨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he-she-me wumbo
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动词原型巨  现在分词巨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wumbo, wumboing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道从这么高的地方摔下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if a fall from this height
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会不会摔死我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would be enough to kill me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wumbology?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨研究
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The study of wumbo?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.95,0:08:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连一年级小朋友都会  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's first grade, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  真对不起我先前质疑你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I'm sorry I doubted you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, all right, then
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let 'er rip
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's giant
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下我能不能变大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I be giant next?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不是我变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I'm not giant
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你也变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've shrunk, too
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好我还有这个腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I've still got this pickle
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你还会带我们去找美人鱼战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now will you take us to Mermaidman?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.15,0:08:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让他发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He can never find out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'll think of something
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,期间你们就安全待在这个罐子里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until then, you'll be safe in this jar
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道还有什么很好笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what's funny?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.75,0:09:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我腌椰菜一开始出了个罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pickle started out in a jar
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在又进了个罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now it's in one again
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像双关笑话什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like a pun or something
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才缩小了俩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only two people
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.92,0:09:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No big deal
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.87,0:09:13.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会有别的目击者了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:13.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody else saw it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.14,0:09:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.60,0:09:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.25,0:09:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,岂有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For cryin'
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did ya'll do to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士进来就
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman came in, and
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.71,0:09:23.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:23.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.95,0:09:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵兄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge-Dude
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:43.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1132,954)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, hi
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.73,0:09:42.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  海绵哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:42.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's up, Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得找个更大的罐子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to get a bigger jar
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  能不能别自己骗自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, will you just face facts?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经把裤头村全体居民都缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've shrunken everybody in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须去找美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to go to Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  他一定会失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, he'll be so disappointed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能害我们永远都这么小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't leave us small forever
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要承认你的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to admit your mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你妈说得对  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your mother's right, son
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman will understand
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是美人鱼战士  老不死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're Mermaidman, you old coot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.52,0:10:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是你的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just that I'm such a big fan
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你的腰带
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your belt
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用怕  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, son
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I understand
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.30,0:10:28.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回想起我第一次用腰带的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:28.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I remember back when I first used the belt
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.68,0:10:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是一九零一一还是一二来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the year was nineteen, aught, eleventy-twelve
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时候的总统应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I believe the president then was
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.67,0:10:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告诉他要怎么把我们放大回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just tell him how to un-shrink us
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对  放大射线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, the un-shrink ray
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你设置成巨了没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you set it to wumbo?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我得开五英里的船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I have to drive five miles
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能去上卫生间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to go to the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是在我自己家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In my own home
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬一级台阶我都得坐电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I need an elevator to climb one stair
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都缩小好多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been shrinking for years
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这也太离谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this is ridiculous
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有东西都太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's too big
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.72,0:11:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我没法放大你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since I couldn't make you big
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就缩小城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made the city small
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在只要再缩小一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now only one more thing to shrink
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.90,0:11:36.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:36.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.77,0:11:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉还行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess this is okay
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  也没多大区别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's the difference?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回家的感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's great to be back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.11,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}坐牢记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:05.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(277.802,370)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(411.802,692)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(379.802,280)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(319.802,350)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.92\pos(469.802,666)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:11.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(708,370)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is the one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, think, think
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往那边转  往那边转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn that way, turn that way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  往那边转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, turn that way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,右转  左转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, left
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.06,0:12:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上转  下转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up, down
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.94,0:12:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  不能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't ever do that
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.42,0:12:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.96,0:12:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行的  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do this, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.27,0:12:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行的  我能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do it, I can do it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾考结束了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The driving test is over, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行的  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do this, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回马路  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The road, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回马路上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back on the road
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要考过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to pass the test
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.17,0:12:34.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:34.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to pass
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,西瓜怎么你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you got against the melons?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定是驾考的夜路部分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be the night-driving part of the test
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要让你端正做好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to straighten you out
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用这个修理你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll fix you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续修那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's get that one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.45,0:12:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位前面没挂车牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy had no front license plate
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.81,0:12:56.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:56.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get him
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.98,0:12:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看那些警察
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:12:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all those police
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道是不是总统来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the president's in town
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我满怀无比自豪的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is with great pride
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.12,0:13:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正式启用这座未完工的大桥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I officially open this unfinished bridge
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪里出错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did I go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:31.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(804,184)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.67,0:13:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我开设了一所新滑浪学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With the opening of my new boating school
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.62,0:13:27.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特此庄严承诺只要有学生愿意学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:27.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I pledge that as long as a student is willing to learn
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就绝不放弃他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shall never give up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,578)}荫凉滩疗养院
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧卸下这一整车的水果潘趣酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with that truckload of fruit punch
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.62,0:13:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老人家都快发癫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The seniors are getting cranky
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.14,0:13:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alive
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm alive
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王  我还
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune, I'm still
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位老人家  大家开窗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, seniors, let's open these windows
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让全世界看见你们洁白的衣装
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so the world can see your nice white clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个适合冲浪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a surfin'
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲浪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surfin'
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲浪的夏天  好一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surfin' summer, it's gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's finally finished
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我白纸红字写的生平回忆录
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A memoir of my life, written in red ink
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.76,0:14:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That depends
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我考过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I pass?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freeze
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能逮捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't arrest him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只是个驾校学员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just a student driver
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们说的不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not talking about him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I don't belong here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是个天大的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all a big mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我也不属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't belong here, either
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.96,0:14:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.80,0:14:50.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:50.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm innocent
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I belong here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.93,0:14:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的  泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can do this, Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能保持理智熬过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can get through this without losing your sanity
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能再走上老路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a road we don't want to go down again
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Positives
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想好处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think of the positives
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.72,0:15:07.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不用评卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:07.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got no more papers to grade
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实  也没工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in fact, no more work
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没有课要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more boating school classes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不用开船了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more driving
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没有海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.32,0:15:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有电话推销了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more phone solicitors
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.72,0:15:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有公司团建百味餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more company potlucks
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有路怒症了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more road rage
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有保费了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more insurance payments
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.07,0:15:30.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:30.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:42.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,164)}裤头村监狱
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.54,0:15:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该会喜欢上这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to like this place
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有泡芙老师的课堂不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Class just isn't the same without Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.38,0:15:51.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想她的处境  在监狱里孤独受怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:51.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just the thought of her, alone and afraid in jail
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.23,0:15:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我想到她在监狱里孤独受怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:52.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It makes me think about her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,being alone and afraid in jail
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道她得怎么安稳活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know how she's going to survive
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轻嗅美丽玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smelling the pretty roses
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸福就像两种冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happiness is just two kinds of ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That poor woman
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's all my fault
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许去找派大星倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I go talk to Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能让我不那么内疚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he can ease my guilt
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来全都要怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it sounds like it's all your fault
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师坐牢了  全都要怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff's in jail, and it's all because of me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真是个缺心眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm such a barnacle-head
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得救她出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get her out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过要想让她出狱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But to get her out of jail
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就得先进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,first we got to get in jail
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How we going to do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.30,0:16:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  把钱放袋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, put the money in the bag
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:39.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,176)}第一航海银行
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put it in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您方向反了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're facing the wrong way, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把钱给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,give me the money
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要从储蓄金里取钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will that be from your savings
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是从活期存款账户取钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or your checking account, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,储蓄金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Savings
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请出示身份证件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I please see some identification?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.10,0:16:54.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:54.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.91,0:16:55.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:55.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(988,282)}捉水母俱乐部会员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(394,802)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  您两个账户余额
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, we are showing a balance
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.19,0:17:04.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,均为零元零角零分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:03.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of zero dollars and zero cents
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for both of your accounts
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.07,0:17:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过程比预想的要顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That went better than expected
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  本来我还以为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I didn't think
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.30,0:17:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没法这么快就能把泡芙老师救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'd get Mrs. Puff out of jail this fast
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.77,0:17:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这次一定能进监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll get into jail this time
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有对石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a couple
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.37,0:17:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲  娘们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your back in it, girls
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.93,0:17:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星你看  她在那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick, there she is
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's us
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝和派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚差点以为那颗黄石头跟我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For a second, I thought that yellow rock talked to me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且声音还很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and its voice sounded a lot like
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.05,0:17:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是要救你出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to bust you out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.21,0:17:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么要跟着我进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you follow me in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你已经是中暑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like this heat's gone to your head
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然这么爱跟石头说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're going to talk to rocks
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就去打饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it's time for you to go on kitchen duty
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定是我中暑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it must be the heat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.82,0:18:10.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:10.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们伪装服的押金付诸东流了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There goes our deposit on these costumes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:24.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,136)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙阿姨好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Puff Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's today's grub?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唐娜好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Donna
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老样子  还是辣椒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's chili, same as always
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你打一些吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me get you some
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.67,0:18:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些可怕的幻觉何时才会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When are these horrific hallucinations going to end?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  真的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's really me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也带派大星过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought Patrick along, too
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们要救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because we're going to set you free
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么带他过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why'd you bring him?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他喜欢辣椒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He likes chili
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  趁没被看到赶紧进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, quick, get in before someone sees
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我不跟你走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I am not going with you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a good one, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.59,0:19:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now hop in, come on
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  她好像是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I think she means it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.00,0:19:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太扯了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's crazy, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说得对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm staying
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like it here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些都是我的同类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are my people
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我坐牢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And besides, if I'm in here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不用再应付你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that means I won't have to deal with you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.67,0:19:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,理会自来水里的铀元素
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Uranium in the water supply
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清澈见底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crystal clear
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.86,0:19:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先失陪一下  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse us just one second, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  她迷失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, she has lost it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她彻底赖在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's completely institutionalized
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都忘了外面生活多逍遥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's forgotten what it's like to live on the outside
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远离牢笼多快活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To not be in prison
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该睡觉了  老公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming to bed, honey?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得让她想起来还有比这更美好的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to remind her there is life other than this
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  跟我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, if you come with us
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就留校布置教室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll stay after school and decorate the whole classroom
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再说最后一遍  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For the last time, no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不跟你们走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not going with you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后通牒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's final
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.22,0:20:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又在跟没生命的物品说话了  泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talking to inanimate objects again, eh, Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回你的牢房去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to your cell
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后不安排你打饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more kitchen time for you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.87,0:20:17.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:17.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hop on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狱警
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guards
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.50,0:20:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狱警
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guards
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.05,0:20:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come quick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前教过的发癫学生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a crazed ex-student of mine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他的胖朋友要来劫我出狱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and his overweight friend here to break me out
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只是做衣架的原材料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just raw material used to make coat hangers
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need some rest
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hop in, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狱警
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guards
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.07,0:20:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狱警
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guards
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.62,0:20:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come look
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我工资低  不负责帮你冲马桶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't pay me enough to do this job
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, up here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.20,0:20:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狱警
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guards
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狱警
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guards
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闹什么闹  泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's all the hubbub, Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.70,0:20:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, it's us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the barnacle is going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在胡言乱语什么  泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们骗不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.07,0:21:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟那个爱吃辣椒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that guy who likes the chili
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.07,0:21:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认了吧  泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's face it, Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经严重越界了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've gone off the deep end
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in there, you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.10,0:21:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好在单独禁闭室里反省一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need a nice long stay in solitary confinement
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.97,0:21:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再往好的方面看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's look at the positives again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于能离那两个远远的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm finally away from those two
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.02,0:21:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  自个儿待在我软绵绵的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, all alone in my nice soft room
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.02,0:21:44.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵做的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:44.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Made of sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能考过的  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can pass the test, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.97,0:21:58.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能考过的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:58.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can pass the test
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freeze
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兜风结束了  混账
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your joyride's over, punk
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.83,0:22:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.70,0:22:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.40,0:22:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.10,0:22:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.62,0:22:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.10,0:22:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.55,0:22:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.07,0:22:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.64,0:22:20.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有只蜗牛得喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a snail to feed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:24.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,554)}警察
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.94,0:22:22.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不能坐牢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't go to jail now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.16,0:22:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别现在就关我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is not a good time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, please
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.26,0:22:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please, I'm not a criminal
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.57,0:22:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.60,0:22:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来只是场梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all a dream
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不用去坐牢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to jail
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.73,0:22:32.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么要去坐牢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:32.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would you go to jail?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.41,0:22:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经坐牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You already did your time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.37,0:22:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来又是我的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just my imagination again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.65,0:22:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天晚上吃什么  泡芙阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what's for dinner tonight, Puff Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.80,0:22:47.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辣椒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:47.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,chili?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.32,0:22:56.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.32,0:22:56.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
